

This directory is for custom libraries used in the Mavlink Bridge project.

## How to Add Libraries

- Place each library in its own folder under `lib/` (e.g., `lib/mavlink_parser/`).
- Add source files and headers for your bridge logic, MAVLink protocol, or hardware drivers.
- Use `library.json` for custom build options if needed.

## Example

- See `lib/mavlink_parser/` for MAVLink parsing code (if present).

## Resources

- PlatformIO Library Manager: https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/index.html

The PlatformIO Library Dependency Finder will find automatically dependent
libraries by scanning project source files.

More information about PlatformIO Library Dependency Finder
- https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/ldf.html
